OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a dry day with
OL,6,Fbright or sunny spells. The odd
OL,7,Fisolated shower possible in the
OL,8,Fafternoon but for the majority it will
OL,9,Fremain dry. Light northwesterly winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FIt will be a dry evening with
OL,12,Flight winds and clear spells. Turning
OL,13,Fcloudier overnight with a few showers,
OL,14,Fthese mainly in east near the coast.
OL,15,
OL,16,CMonday:FA largely cloudy day with
OL,17,Foutbreaks of showery rain possible.
OL,18,FShowers may become heavy in places
OL,19,Fthrough the afternoon. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
