OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FHigh
OL,6,Fpressure dominates bringing a dry and
OL,7,Fsettled few days with light winds.
OL,8,FPlenty of bright and sunny spells, but
OL,9,Fit often cloudier near the coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
